    "The six main characters dominate both measures, with Joey, Ross, Rachel, Chandler, Phoebe, and Monica all appearing near the top. The top-10 overlap has **7 shared nodes**, indicating that brokerage and recursive importance largely agree in this network. Smaller differences, such as guest characters appearing in one list but not the other, add role-specific nuance.\n"
   ]
