  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "37c63e4a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### **6.4 Export for Gephi Lite**\n",
    "\n",
    "The selected partition is exported as node and edge tables plus a GEXF file. These files can be opened in Gephi Lite for external inspection and styling.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "42506a49",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
